FBIS4-60144 "drnes099_n_94009" FBIS-NES-94-099 Daily Report 21 May 1994 LEBANON Reaction to al-Dirani Seizure Reported Reaction to al-Dirani Seizure Reported Al-Tufayli Blames Government NC2105163194 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1530 GMT 21 May 94 NC2105163194 Beirut Radio Lebanon Arabic BFN [Text] Hizballah vehicles roamed the streets of Western Ba'labakk and the international highway using loudspeakers to condemn the Israeli operation and global arrogance. A demonstration was staged in Brital to condemn the operation. [Former Hizballah Secretary General] Shaykh Subhi al-Tufayli addressed the demonstrators, lambasting the Lebanese Government and holding it responsible.
